title: Make Quail Chase Your New Home. Reserve Your 2 Bedroom Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Here at Quail Chase Apartments, you’ll enjoy worry free living, open & spacious floor plans, remote access private garage spaces and a beautifully landscaped community.', 'You will love our friendly on-site management and maintenance team.', 'Each home at Quail Chase was designed with you in mind, featuring ample countertop & cabinet space, 9’ foot ceilings and garden bathtubs for extra comfort.', 'Our community is also pet friendly', 'so you don’t have to leave your furry friends behind!', 'Voucher Holders Welcome!*', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- State-Of-The-Art Fitness Center', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Pre-Wired For Intrusion Alarm System', '- Covered Pavilion With BBQ & Lounge Area', '- Designer Lighting Package', '- Large Walk-In Closet(s)', '- Six Panel Doors', '- Community Library', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Quail Chase participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $37,260 | 2 Occupants: $43,540 | 3 Occupants: $47,880 | 4 Occupants: $53,160 | 5 Occupants: $557,420 | 6 Occupants: $61,680.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Quail Chase', '500 W. Airtex', 'Houston, TX, 77090', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '6AOSn1wk4']
